# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# C64 binary content: belt-and-suspenders.
# Blanket-block every .d64 and .prg in the tree, then explicitly whitelist
# the few that are safe to ship. This means an accidental `git add .` from
# the repo root with a stray .d64 sitting anywhere will refuse to add it
# instead of leaking it.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.d64
*.prg

# Test fixtures (frozen content, edited via tests only)
!tests/disks/BlankDisk.d64
!tests/disks/gmc64-test.d64

# Public-facing demo disks (curated content, may evolve over time)
!disks/
!disks/**
